<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٣٢ ... سُورَةُ السَّجْدَةِ ... آياتها ٣٠ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{افْتَرَاهُ}</span> ... اخْتَلَقَهُ مِنْ عِنْدِ نَفْسِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَوَى}</span> ... عَلَا وَارْتَفَعَ؛ اسْتِوَاءً يَلِيقُ بِجَلَالِهِ وَعَظَمَتِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعْرُجُ إِلَيْهِ}</span> ... يَصْعَدُ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَسْلَهُ}</span> ... ذُرِّيَّتَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلَالَةٍ}</span> ... وَهِيَ النُّطْفَةُ؛ لِأَنَّهَا مُسْتَلَّةٌ مِنْ جَمِيعِ البَدَنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّهِينٍ}</span> ... ضَعِيفٍ، رَقِيقٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَلَلْنَا فِي الْأَرْضِ}</span> ... تَحَوَّلْنَا تُرَابًا بَعْدَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَاكِسُو رُؤُوسِهِمْ}</span> ... قَدْ خَفَضُوهَا، وَأَطْرَقُوا خِزْيًا وَنَدَمًا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَقَّ الْقَوْلُ}</span> ... ثَبَتَ وَتَحَقَّقَ وَوَجَبَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْجِنَّةِ}</span> ... الجِنِّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَتَجَافَى}</span> ... تَرْتَفِعُ، وَتَتَنحَّى لِلْعِبَادَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَضَاجِعِ}</span> ... فُرُشِ النَّوْمِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّا أُخْفِيَ لَهُم}</span> ... مَا ادُّخِرَ لَهُمْ مِنَ الجَزَاءِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِّن قُرَّةِ أَعْيُنٍ}</span> ... مَا يُفْرِحُ، وَيَسُرُّ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَاوَى}</span> ... الَّتِي يَاوُونَ إِلَيْهَا، وَيُقِيمُونَ بِهَا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُزُلًا}</span> ... ضِيَافَةً لَهُمْ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>